(DarkMouse and GoldenEye are pred)

DarkMouse::
She growled slightly. "Ladies? Did you call us ladies?"

Darkmouse and GoldenEye looked at each other with a half twisted 
smile. 

DarkMouse::
She looked at the two bot. "Honey flows quickly from the lips of a 
male when he wants something. But the honey is never long lived. So 
what do you want?"


GoldenEye::
she saw the look that Koj gave her. She smiled at him, showing no 
fear towards him. She looked him up and down,"Hmmm, no weapons, what 
kind of bot walks around without weapoons?" She shook her head, 
showing her disbelief.


::KitKat::
Still tied up in her meeting, she noticed that DarkMouse and 
GoldenEye were outside with two bots.  It showed then talking on her 
little wrist monitor. She sighed and opened her link to DM.
"Show them to the mess hall, I'll be ther when I can."

DarkMouse::
She got the message and looked at the bots."Well, she called. I'll 
take you to the mess hall and you can wait for here there."
She motioned with her hand, the one with the gun, for them to follow 
her. She muttered, "males, can't shoot them all and can't recycle 
them."

GoldenEye::
She kept a close eye on Koj.  She walked in back and took the rear 
position in the escort. "I wouldn't try anything.  The autoguns will 
fire. And you are being heavily monitored."
